[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m942[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn TRUE;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m943[0m[39m:    [0m[39melse[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m944[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m945[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibfreerdp/crypto/x509_utils.[0m[1;92mc:450[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m459[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m450[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->type == GEN_DNS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m451[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Allocate string length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m for security[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m452[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mdns_name = [0m[1;35mmalloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39m [0m[1;35mstrlen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->d.dNSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m453[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m454[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m455[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mgoto end;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m456[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m457[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->d.dNSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m458[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_length[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->d.dNSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m459[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `x509_validate_subject_aternative_names`, the code uses [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mstrlen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` for allocation but then copies [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_length[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` bytes. Because ASN.[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m strings are not guaranteed to be [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNUL-terminated, `strlen` may undercount and the `memcpy` overruns the buffer.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Moreover, after copying, the buffer is never NUL-terminated, so `verify_san`, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich calls `strlen` and indexes through the buffer, can read and validate beyond [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mits bounds.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Finally, the function ignores its own `result` flag: it always returns `TRUE`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meven if `verify_san` fails.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Overview:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Allocate based on `[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_length[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Copy exactly `length` bytes and then explicitly NUL-terminate.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Free the temporary buffer in all paths and reset the pointer to NULL.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. Return the accumulated `result` instead of the hardcoded `TRUE`.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Within the `for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < count; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```c[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         dns_name = [0m[1;35mmalloc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mstrlen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name,[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_length[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        with:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```c[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t len = [0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_length[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->d.dNSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         const unsigned char* data = [0m[1;35mASN1_STRING_get0_data[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgen_name->d.dNSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         dns_name = [0m[1;35mmalloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlen + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!dns_name[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             goto cleanup;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name, data, len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         dns_name[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mlen[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[32m'\0'[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This ensures the buffer is sized correctly and NUL-terminated for safe use [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby `[0m[1;35mverify_san[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. After `[0m[1;35mverify_san[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, always call `[0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and set `dns_name [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m= NULL;` before continuing or exiting.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Rename the cleanup label to `cleanup:` [0m[1;39m([0m[39minstead of `end:`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and update control[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflow:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cleanup:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdns_name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msan_names[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35msk_GENERAL_NAME_pop_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39msan_names, GENERAL_NAME_free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return result;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Initialize `result = TRUE` at the top. On any `verify_san` failure, set [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`result = FALSE` and `goto cleanup;`.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Remove the final `return TRUE;` and replace with `return result;`.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Functionality:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We preserve the iteration over SAN entries, the use of `verify_san` FSM, and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting free logic.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The only external dependencies are OpenSSL macros [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ASN1_STRING_length`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ASN1_STRING_get0_data`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m already in use; no external libraries or harness code are [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodified.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Allocating with the exact ASN.[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m string length and appending a NUL byte [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents the [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m-byte write from overrunning a [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m-byte buffer.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Explicit NUL-termination protects `verify_san`’s `strlen` and bounds-check FSM[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom reading garbage or triggering undefined behavior.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Returning `result` propagates actual validation failures instead of masking [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthem.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Memory usage: we allocate slightly more [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlen+[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but this is minimal. All [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocations are freed immediately.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Behavior change: callers can now observe a `FALSE` return if any SAN entry [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfails validation. This aligns with the original intent of a “validate” function.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes are made to harness or test code, so existing tests and fuzz [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtargets remain valid.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Reference Pattern:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mirror `extract_string`’s use of `ASN1_STRING_to_UTF8`, which allocates a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNUL-terminated buffer; here we manually replicate that pattern using [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ASN1_STRING_length` and `ASN1_STRING_get0_data`.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis strategy fully eliminates the buffer overflow, ensures safe string handling, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand respects existing code architecture without touching harness or external [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdependencies.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                   [0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=713502;file:///home/qqor/aixcc/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=246789;file:///home/qqor/aixcc/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0mn evals: [1;36m5[0m, patch status: PatchStatus.SOUND[1m)[0m                                        [2m               [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/qqor/aixcc/crete/reports/prism.prism_o4_mini/freerdp_fp-delta-02_vuln_002/[0m[95magen[0m [2m               [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95mt-output-1766653193.546452[0m                                                           [2m               [0m
